# per interval → per-chrom concat) → position-based CONSENSUS per chrom
# → Consensus.vcf.gz.
#
# REMOVED vs GATK3 predecessor: RealignerTargetCreator + IndelRealigner
# (GATK4 HaplotypeCaller local reassembly subsumes them).
